    public class MultisetUnion
extends ca.uqac.lif.cep.functions.BinaryFunction<Multiset,Multiset,Multiset>
    Binary function taking as input two multisets, and returning as its output a new multiset containing all elements of both. This should be contrasted with MultisetAddAll.
